    "help.title":  "√Ę¬Ě‚Äú Help Strong GR √Ę‚Ä†‚Äô CZ",
    "help.about":  "What the app does",
    "help.about.body":  "This tool translates Strong dictionary entries (Greek/Hebrew) into Czech in batches via AI providers (`Groq`, `Gemini`, `OpenRouter`). It can save progress, stop AUTO by token limit, import/export TXT/JSON, and retry failed items.",
    "help.keys":  "How to get API keys",
    "help.keys.body":  "`Groq`: create a key at \u003ca href=\"https://console.groq.com/keys\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003econsole.groq.com/keys\u003c/a\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e`Gemini`: create a key at \u003ca href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eAI Studio\u003c/a\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e`OpenRouter`: create a key at \u003ca href=\"https://openrouter.ai/keys\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003eopenrouter.ai/keys\u003c/a\u003e.\u003cbr\u003eThen paste the key into API field and save it to library with \u003cb\u003eSave key\u003c/b\u003e.",
    "help.library":  "API key library",
    "help.library.body":  "You can have multiple keys per provider. Choose a key in the dropdown under API field and switch it in one click. Active key is used for translation and limit checks.",
    "help.limits":  "Limits and quotas",
    "help.limits.body":  "Button `√įŇł‚ÄúŇ† Limits` shows available provider credit/limit data with extra estimates. Some providers do not expose all metrics, so live data and fallback info are combined.\u003cbr\u003eOpenRouter has specific limits for `:free` models (RPM/RPD). After credit top-up (often around 10 USD in current docs), daily free limit can increase, but minute limit and endpoint availability can still differ by model.",
    "help.close":  "√ĘŇď‚ÄĘ Close",
